# Entity

## Notice

### FEATURES

extends = ["SimpleEntity"]

### ATTRIBUTE

| name          | type   | multiplicity | web-label | web-control-type | web-placeholder | web-help                         | web-min-length | web-max-length | web-pattern          |
|---------------+--------+--------------+-----------+------------------+-----------------+----------------------------------+----------------+----------------+----------------------|
| senderName    | string | 1            | Sender    |                  | Your name       | Name displayed as the poster.    | 1              |                |                      |
