| title         | string | 1            | Title     |                  | Short title     | Short title shown in lists.      | 1              | 80             | pass:[^[A-Za-z0-9 ]+$] |
| content       | string | 1            | Content   | textarea         | Notice content  | Main notice text.                | 1              |                |                      |
